  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Evil has come to Feldspar Fields, but geological forces have teamed up
    to defend the lands. Build towers and defeat all four waves of enemies to secure
    the land. Do not let the enemies destroy the castle or else you must start the
    level over. Earn gold to purchase towers and upgrades. Gold is earned passively
    over time, from defeating enemies, advancing through zones, and from purchased
    gold mines.\n\nYou start with three buildable objects.\n1. Amethyst Shooter --
    single target, high damage\n2. Magma Tower -- medium damage, burns over time\n3.
    Deep Mine -- no damage, but grants income every second\n\nUse the num keys to
    select a tower to plant over the square you are standing on. Move your builder
    with WASD or arrow keys. Upgrades may be purchased by clicking their respective
    buttons. These upgrades go with you through levels. \n   HINT: It's often better
    to prioritize upgrades since you cannot take towers or mines with you into other
    zones."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
